<div class="prose mx-auto">

<p>Hello! My name is Arun. Since I was a child, I have tried and failed to learn Tamil, the
language of my ancestors. There are so few resources for spoken Tamil that it is hard to begin and
even harder to continue. But with the love and encouragement of my wonderful Tamil-speaking wife,
I finally broke through.</p>



<p>This site contains some of the resources I made for my own studies. I want to improve and polish
what's here, but only if there is enough interest and commitment to make the effort worthwhile.
<a class="font-bold hover:text-blue-500" href="https://forms.gle/zXA777erK3WWmzDv9">If you want more, please join my mailing
list</a>!</p>

<p>Current resources:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="/tamil/sounds/">Sounds</a> &mdash; A short guide to the sounds of spoken
  Tamil and how to pronounce them.</li>

  <li><a href="/tamil/words/">Words</a> &mdash; More than 1500 Tamil words grouped by
  category with simple definitions.</li>
  
</ul>


</div>

